Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_jena

Interface TextExtractor

All Known Implementing Classes:
TextExtractorAllAnnotationProperties, TextExtractorAllLiterals, TextExtractorAllStringLiterals, TextExtractorFallback, TextExtractorForTransformers, TextExtractorMultipleProperties, TextExtractorProperty, TextExtractorSet, TextExtractorShortAndLongTexts, TextExtractorUrlFragment, TextExtractorUrlLocalName, TextExtractorUseLongestLiteralOrFragment
public interface TextExtractor
Given a Jena resource, a ValueExtractor can derive zero or more String representations. Developer remark: If you implement a new extractor: For a good design, you may want to implement a LiteralExtractor and use this interface to wrap it. Code for wrapping: extractor.extract(resource).stream().map(Literal::getLexicalForm).filter(x -> !x.trim().equals("")).collect(Collectors.toSet());
